Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,== 字幕制作：wolfkin ==
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们出生在这个世界之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.21,0:00:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球是多么的灿烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.98,0:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们在离开这个世界之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.68,0:00:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球依旧是多么的灿烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.22,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们于活着的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.52,0:00:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仰望着星海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想着自己的将来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.29,0:01:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们一面仰望着星海\n一面继续着旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.20,0:01:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并追求着无法实现的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.27,0:01:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有尽头的旅程很遥远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.31,0:01:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们终究于追求理想的旅程中\n永远的沉睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.05,0:01:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们的死亡\n人们的出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.88,0:01:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一切尚未结束的时光中\n列车继续的奔驰着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.56,0:01:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一切尚未结束的铁轨上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.96,0:01:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,载着梦想、希望、野心及年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.60,0:01:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在列车也持续的奔驰着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.68,0:02:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在有位年轻人正启程去\n实现它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.59,0:02:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银河铁道999
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.38,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起的话比较不会那么显目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.22,0:05:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无期间限制之地方铁道的\n全线车票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\n乘坐银河铁道999特快列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.59,0:05:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.13,0:05:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿郎\n接住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊！我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕你这个现行犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\n放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再挣扎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.29,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈…妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！接着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.89,0:07:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,项链…还我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开往大都会区的\n宇宙特快末班列车进站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.64,0:10:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.85,0:11:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有机械身体就不会怕冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.29,0:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有机械身体就能活得很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.33,0:11:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\n只要定时交换零件就能长生不老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.84,0:11:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸如果还活着的话\n就会买机械身体给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们也要到大都会区\n去坐999特急列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.12,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要有很多钱买车票呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点我了解…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.19,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力工作赚很多钱\n坐999列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后到免费供应机械身体的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.27,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎你真是的\n好像马上会实现一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.54,0:11:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊\n我一定会实现我的梦想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.98,0:12:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.23,0:12:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪开\n铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快逃.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.03,0:13:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械伯爵有时会以捕捉\n人类为乐趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.57,0:13:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉人类…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.21,0:13:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一带是机械伯爵的领土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.65,0:13:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以把人类当猎物杀了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.66,0:13:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作！振作啊！妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.56,0:13:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\n我们要一起逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.11,0:13:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后就只剩铁郎一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.41,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈相信…\n铁郎很坚强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.35,0:13:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要努力取得机械身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这一带没有错？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵\n在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.81,0:14:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起\n我没有看过这么美丽的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒的猎物\n就装饰在客厅的墙壁上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定会对它赞不绝口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.14,0:14:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！\n回到时间城聚会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.45,0:15:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.22,0:15:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大都会区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎正睡着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.89,0:16:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.06,0:16:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何你绝对不能离开他半步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须像影子紧紧地\n跟着那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可违逆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.57,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的使命\n梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.28,0:16:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子？\n是指我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.33,0:16:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事！我听到怪声\n所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我确实有听到声音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.25,0:17:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那她到底是何方神圣？\n又拥有人类身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又和妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自言自语什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\n我刚好梦到我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.63,0:17:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦？\n也许是那梦境机器的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.41,0:17:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这台机器可以看到睡梦中\n梦境的机器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到我的梦吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候如果不管你的话\n你就会被警察抓走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.64,0:18:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道当小偷不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.42,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你一定要坐上\n999特急列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.19,0:18:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要拿到机械身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到机械身体又怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了机械伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.31,0:18:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我的车票给你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前，这个先还你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.72,0:18:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么在乎你妈妈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.09,0:18:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦！\n梅德尔你也有妈妈吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该会了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.57,0:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会你妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.14,0:19:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚遇到你时\n我很讶异你这么像我妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说999列车的车票要送我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会不会骗我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要取得机械身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后为了跟机械伯爵决斗\n而想坐上999列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.54,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道虎克船长及\n亚迈拉尔达丝的事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.38,0:19:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要像虎克及亚迈拉尔达丝一样\n自由的在星海里游走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.32,0:19:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到机械身体后就可以长生不老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想永远地在星海里旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是男人的本色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.33,0:20:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎克及亚迈拉尔达丝\n是你们年轻人的偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.81,0:20:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要给我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是有条件的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,条件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.05,0:20:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去安卓美达\n免费供应机械身体的星球时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也一起带我去的话\n我就送你这张车票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.99,0:20:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.23,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也对\n女人自己去的话太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会带我一起去吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.53,0:20:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里签上你的名字\n那这张车票就是你的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那签上你的名字吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.28,0:20:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星野铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很男性化的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我爸爸帮我取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以坐上999列车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这张车票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.90,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使梅德尔是巫女\n被杀了就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.94,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能坐上999列车到免费\n供应机械身体的星球就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.65,0:21:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门！里面有藏匿活生生犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们了解吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.89,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.49,0:21:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦坐上银河铁道999列车后\n就没办法中途折返地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.93,0:21:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到安卓美达的途中下车的话\n只有一辈子在那个星球等死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎\n你的命运就是其中之一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会后悔吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.48,0:22:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不后悔的\n现在最重要的就是坐上999列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.67,0:22:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请注意\n请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.37,0:22:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零时出发往安卓美达\n乘坐999特急列车的旅客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.48,0:22:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请尽速至第99月台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.38,0:22:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0时18分往火星的郊外线\n请到第25月台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.06,0:22:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2时15分往大麦哲伦的旅客\n请到第75月台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.07,0:23:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是有名的银河铁道999列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.04,0:23:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\n很惊讶吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.08,0:23:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…这么老式的列车…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.45,0:23:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.59,0:23:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是由耐热能无限电磁防护罩\n所保护的超近代宇宙列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.09,0:23:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是外观故意做成古老的\n蒸气火车头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.44,0:23:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？安心了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.95,0:23:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了那些再也回不来的旅客们\n这类型的古老列车最适合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.53,0:24:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了机械身体后\n一定会回来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.91,0:24:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的男孩踏上\n一辈子只有一次的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.65,0:24:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无畏惧感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.92,0:24:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是令你一辈子\n都无法忘记的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.12,0:24:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎\n你的旅途即将开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.10,0:25:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于踏上旅途了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.47,0:25:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.74,0:25:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.34,0:25:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:15.48,0:28:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好趁现在多看几眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:20.19,0:28:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定下次回来\n你就只能用机械人的眼睛看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.60,0:28:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了\n不用看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.20,0:28:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道悲伤的回忆令你难过\n但或许也会有怀念的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.90,0:28:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好你会很庆幸多看几眼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.11,0:28:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就等老的时候\n再来后悔好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.78,0:28:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我只想要机械身体了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:45.65,0:28:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想要…有机械身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.16,0:29:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一站停靠‘泰坦星’\n‘泰坦星’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.57,0:29:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停车时间是地球时间16天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.54,0:29:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,16天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.34,0:29:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停车时间要16天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.91,0:29:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.47,0:29:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.44,0:29:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦是土星的卫星之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:16.21,0:29:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是太阳系中的第二大行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.68,0:29:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说大小的话\n它直径5800公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:24.69,0:29:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自转周期为16天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.49,0:29:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每站的停车时间是那星球的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:32.13,0:29:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说有些需停车10小时\n有些则需50小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:36.73,0:29:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.30,0:29:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说自转速度各有不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:42.70,0:29:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停车期间我们可以\n自由下车去参观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.17,0:29:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不会无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:46.54,0:29:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果错过开车时间\n坐不上车的话就会死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.81,0:29:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死掉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:52.75,0:29:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是被丢下的人\n是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:55.62,0:29:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真严格啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.65,0:30:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，银河铁道999列车\n是很遵守规定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.10,0:30:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦是太阳系中最美的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.07,0:30:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是非常可怕的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.04,0:30:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像以前在氨水的液态沼泽之中\n隐现的小岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:23.85,0:30:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的泰坦有着完全不能以\n别的星球的常理来判断自然环境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.62,0:30:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们花很多时间努力的\n把它塑造成绿色星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.72,0:30:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用尽血汉努力着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:03.69,0:31:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的地方！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.10,0:31:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.04,0:31:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.71,0:31:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.21,0:31:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎不要过来\n不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.84,0:31:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.61,0:32:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.15,0:32:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.55,0:32:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.89,0:32:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.05,0:32:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是跟你一起的女孩吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.49,0:32:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被掳走了…\n被葡萄谷的山贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.60,0:32:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山贼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.86,0:32:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没冷掉之前先喝了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.41,0:32:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在车站有人被杀\n还有梅德尔被抓走都没有人管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.05,0:32:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么鬼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.78,0:32:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在泰坦想做什么事都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.78,0:32:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人只要想做什么\n就可以自由自在的去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.82,0:32:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是这个星球的法律\n‘乐园法’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.13,0:32:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‘乐园法’！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.96,0:32:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那梅德尔怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.47,0:32:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葡萄谷的山贼在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:58.33,0:33:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去救她只是陪了性命罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:02.27,0:33:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚遇到梅德尔时\n我答应要帮她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.01,0:33:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她才让我搭上银河铁道999列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.71,0:33:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一定要救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.75,0:33:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葡萄谷的山贼在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:11.08,0:33:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.52,0:33:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葡萄谷在河川的下游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.49,0:33:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐那艘船去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.46,0:33:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.79,0:33:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.84,0:33:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,土星的光线很强\n可别晒昏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.94,0:33:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个也给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:43.68,0:33:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这把枪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:45.15,0:33:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会保护你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.68,0:33:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么气派的枪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:52.19,0:33:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去救她\n否则天快暗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.64,0:34:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是环境再舒适的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.74,0:34:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么都能自由去做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.07,0:34:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类还真有办法把它\n弄得天昏地暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.11,0:34:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命！救命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.49,0:34:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.85,0:34:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好\n没事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.38,0:34:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.58,0:35:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:27.82,0:35:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.69,0:35:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.85,0:35:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.02,0:35:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吵啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:36.02,0:35:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小子是我们的救命恩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.83,0:35:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼\n你这把战士的枪从哪里来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:50.11,0:35:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战士的枪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.71,0:35:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这把宇宙枪能打倒机械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.85,0:36:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这把枪能打倒机械人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.02,0:36:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这把？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.02,0:36:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这把枪从哪里来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.92,0:36:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里拿到的都不打紧\n先告诉我梅德尔在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.32,0:36:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼\n小心你的态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.33,0:36:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女人在我们手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.30,0:36:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好不要忘记我们是山贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.57,0:36:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.40,0:36:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要一直叫我小鬼\n我的名字叫做星野铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.14,0:36:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:26.68,0:36:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会喜欢那个叫\n梅德尔的女人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.85,0:36:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:33.11,0:36:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我约定好要保护她\n才坐上999列车的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:37.75,0:36:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,999列车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.65,0:36:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会也想拿到机械身体吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:42.52,0:36:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为了打倒机械伯爵才这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.56,0:36:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.73,0:36:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…\n放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:52.10,0:36:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\n放开我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.97,0:38:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼是不是人类照了就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:03.41,0:38:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不是人类\n有可能会暗杀我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.08,0:38:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.69,0:38:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼是不折不扣的人类身躯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.26,0:38:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:26.80,0:38:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.93,0:38:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是机械人的话\n我就把你分尸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.45,0:38:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\n害你不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.12,0:38:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的确是…人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.36,0:39:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一家人\n对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:04.70,0:39:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了表示赔罪\n也让你瞧瞧我的骨骼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.91,0:39:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.34,0:39:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在各个星球的战场及抢劫现场\n中留在体内的能源未爆弹头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.18,0:39:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一有一天它们爆了的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:23.82,0:39:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就什么也不剩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.99,0:39:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也挺不错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.11,0:39:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是他们的家\n儿童们的天堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.64,0:39:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儿童们的天堂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.51,0:39:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些小孩是….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.75,0:39:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.15,0:39:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤儿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.48,0:39:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.28,0:39:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的父母跟你一样\n被机械伯爵杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:02.36,0:40:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道机械伯爵住哪里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.06,0:40:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是叫做时间城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.53,0:40:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间城在哪个星球没有人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:11.47,0:40:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…只有一个人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:16.40,0:40:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.64,0:40:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是女海贼亚迈拉尔达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.74,0:40:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚迈拉尔达丝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:21.64,0:40:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没看过像她这么可怕的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.85,0:40:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找她被怎么样都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:29.18,0:40:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才可以见到\n亚迈拉尔达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.19,0:40:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要担心\n你一定会见到她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:37.83,0:40:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:45.50,0:40:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好喝吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.24,0:40:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要告诉你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:49.00,0:40:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你遇到机械伯爵\n一定要先发致胜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:53.78,0:40:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使对方流泪哀求\n必要之际一定得狠下心开枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:57.78,0:41:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则输的就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.92,0:41:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在宇宙中生存的必要的条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.09,0:41:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.59,0:41:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.84,0:41:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你终于平安回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:29.08,0:41:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\n多亏这把枪救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.11,0:41:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这把枪你以后还会用到\n送给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:37.61,0:41:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说这是战士的枪\n是婆婆你的宝物吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:42.62,0:41:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这把枪送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:44.65,0:41:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:45.82,0:41:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是我唯一的儿子的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.32,0:41:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪跟帽子曾经伴着我儿子\n渡过了无数次的危险和死亡边缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.10,0:42:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他却丢下了它走了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.14,0:42:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你遇到他的话\n记得告诉他要回家看父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:13.21,0:42:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在临终之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:23.86,0:42:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你儿子叫什么名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:27.60,0:42:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是…\n他也戴着我做的帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.00,0:42:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你在宇宙任何一角落\n遇到他的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:36.14,0:42:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到他的话\n我一定会告诉他你在等他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.14,0:42:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道\n他应该不可能活着回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.15,0:42:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也没有机会告诉他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.85,0:42:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解的\n身为妈妈的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.59,0:42:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子是男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.13,0:43:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为男人之身\n没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.33,0:43:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下站…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:36.40,0:43:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下站停靠‘冥王星’‘冥王星’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.17,0:43:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停车时间是6.39日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:00.86,0:44:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是‘冥王星’啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:02.99,0:44:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的旅客称它为彷徨之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:07.93,0:44:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨之星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.23,0:44:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寒冷…永久冰冻的\n最边缘的小行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.94,0:44:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪…这么冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.54,0:44:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人说是被冰冻在星球上的\n旅人的鬼魂在作崇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:35.19,0:44:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:10.22,0:45:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈从前在雪中\n也是这样帮我取暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:17.43,0:45:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…好像跟妈妈在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:54.60,0:45:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，我要去办事\n你先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:59.14,0:46:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要走出街道以外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.64,0:46:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街道以内都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.48,0:46:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有带枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.01,0:46:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有枪也不行\n太冷了没办法用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:23.02,0:47:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:24.59,0:47:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫夏都，是这冰坟的管理员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:29.80,0:47:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰坟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:34.24,0:47:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是病死在此地的旅客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:36.17,0:47:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是更换机械身体\n而抛下原本身体的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:40.04,0:47:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类残骸长眠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:42.91,0:47:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的…残骸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:51.85,0:47:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:53.49,0:47:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎\n我想让你看看以前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:58.63,0:48:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里换了机械身体\n到别的星球后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:04.57,0:48:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为想念以前的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:07.13,0:48:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想和以前的身体一起\n就回到此地当管理员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:11.71,0:48:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我…\n我的身体快冻僵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:14.61,0:48:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:17.78,0:48:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:20.15,0:48:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是以前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:22.88,0:48:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连机械体都没办法造得如此完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:26.95,0:48:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有一张脸能够满足我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.32,0:48:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以到最后都没造出脸来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.19,0:48:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此人们叫我彷徨之星的夏都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:39.63,0:48:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:40.33,0:48:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:46.44,0:48:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我…\n你要我怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:49.81,0:48:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…只想要你陪在我身体旁…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:53.11,0:48:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:54.08,0:48:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要\n放开我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:55.72,0:48:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息吧！小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:02.22,0:49:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开她\n夏都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:08.83,0:49:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏都\n是你自己要换成机械身体的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:14.30,0:49:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只因为自己寂寞\n而要连累别人未免太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:19.24,0:49:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有勇气变回原来的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:22.04,0:49:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要长生不老还是当人类？\n你根本没有勇气去选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:26.25,0:49:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了\n梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:35.42,0:49:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去了！铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:53.31,0:50:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会有厌倦机械体的人\n回来换回身体也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:01.42,0:50:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里长眠的残骸也许比\n失去身体的机械人还要幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.06,0:50:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔\n这样说好像你就是机械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:16.23,0:50:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为看了夏都后\n才有这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:48.26,0:50:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔刚才在冰坟看什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:53.33,0:50:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔到底是什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:56.84,0:50:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:13.35,0:51:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道梅德尔又怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.22,0:51:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:18.13,0:51:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不知道也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:27.07,0:51:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:57.06,0:51:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:58.13,0:52:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没坐在这么干净的\n椅子上吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:04.47,0:52:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:10.04,0:52:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是玻璃…还是压克力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.65,0:52:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体是水晶玻璃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:15.98,0:52:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:17.25,0:52:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:18.29,0:52:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:18.95,0:52:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:25.76,0:52:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多吃些东西补充体力\n铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:30.70,0:52:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:38.14,0:52:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问决定好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:40.64,0:52:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:43.11,0:52:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎\n吃牛排好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:46.11,0:52:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对对对\n二份牛排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:48.45,0:52:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要几分熟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:52.15,0:52:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分熟还要玉米汤及面包\n还有他要饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:58.03,0:52:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:58.96,0:53:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:05.23,0:53:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的身体跟冥王星的夏朵差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:08.34,0:53:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是总觉得克莉亚比较温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:10.50,0:53:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:11.64,0:53:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你喜欢克莉亚吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:15.58,0:53:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.08,0:53:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎你是不是有什么问题呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.12,0:53:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:24.75,0:53:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎对你的水晶玻璃身体\n很有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:29.76,0:53:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲因为贪图好看而将我\n换成这种玻璃身体….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:36.43,0:53:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只好在这里打工存钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:40.37,0:53:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后去冥王星换回活生生身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:44.44,0:53:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你的身体在冰坟的下面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:47.11,0:53:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:48.08,0:53:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候会趁工作的空档\n回去冥王星看以前的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:54.28,0:53:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么漂亮的身体竟然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:56.32,0:53:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:57.89,0:53:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的身体…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:01.56,0:54:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光线和影子只会从我的身体穿过\n这让我觉得很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:16.97,0:54:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手很温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:29.18,0:54:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停电了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:30.58,0:54:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入隧道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:32.15,0:54:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隧道？这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.99,0:54:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,列车在通过小行星带的时候\n会经过宇宙隧道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:38.13,0:54:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隧道里照明系统会暂时停止运作\n并关闭保险开关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:46.20,0:54:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像萤火虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:47.57,0:54:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来我的身体\n也能够稍微温暖一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:58.91,0:55:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:00.51,0:55:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很满意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.45,0:55:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去付钱\n铁郎你先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:06.35,0:55:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我来带路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:21.03,0:55:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:22.14,0:55:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来我自己回去就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:24.34,0:55:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:30.24,0:55:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又进入隧道了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:31.18,0:55:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已过了隧道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:36.38,0:55:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车长先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:37.88,0:55:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:38.99,0:55:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:40.75,0:55:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\n有不明的船并行的飞过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:45.89,0:55:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船\n是那艘吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:47.76,0:55:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:52.93,0:55:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.11,0:56:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是女海贼亚迈拉尔达丝\n就在你们旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:06.98,0:56:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,999列车请放慢速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:26.87,0:56:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚迈拉尔达丝\n我有事情问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:30.34,0:56:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:32.57,0:56:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:46.95,0:56:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:53.92,0:57:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁射击了我的船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:03.90,0:58:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能没有人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:09.54,0:58:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快站出来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:16.54,0:58:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:18.01,0:58:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你\n想领奖金吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:22.75,0:58:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向我射击的男人\n没有一个逃得过我的魔掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:41.54,0:58:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用结束生命吓唬你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:45.17,0:58:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是小孩子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:56.02,0:58:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这把枪从哪里拿到的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:59.25,0:59:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从泰坦的老婆婆那里得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:02.06,0:59:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有帽子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:03.29,0:59:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帽子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:04.93,0:59:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这顶帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:09.73,0:59:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:16.60,0:59:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道这把枪及帽子\n的主人在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.55,0:59:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:33.72,0:59:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔\n你好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:35.62,0:59:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.99,0:59:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系\n亚迈拉尔达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:40.43,0:59:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:41.29,0:59:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都没听说\n你认识亚迈拉尔达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:46.47,0:59:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我不说\n而是我觉得会遇到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:49.47,0:59:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚迈拉尔达丝\n铁郎有事问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:53.67,0:59:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:54.98,1:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人说你知道\n机械伯爵的时间城在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:00.15,1:00:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械伯爵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:01.95,1:00:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道\n请告诉铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:05.65,1:00:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道又怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.69,1:00:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要杀了他吗？\n要杀机械伯爵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.09,1:00:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:15.03,1:00:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道请告诉他\n亚迈拉尔达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:19.00,1:00:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:21.87,1:00:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以告诉他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:29.74,1:00:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械伯爵的时间城
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.15,1:00:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要增加夥伴\n所以在托列达的分岐点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:41.99,1:00:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托列达的分岐点？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.02,1:00:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是下一个停靠站
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:45.16,1:00:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:49.60,1:00:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫铁郎吧？\n好好珍惜自己仅有的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:59.11,1:01:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚迈拉尔达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:05.21,1:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.50,1:01:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要向你说声谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:31.30,1:01:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果梅德尔跟亚迈拉尔达丝\n不是朋友的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:34.11,1:01:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能会被亚迈拉尔达丝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:38.55,1:01:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:40.58,1:01:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚迈拉尔达丝\n正在找铁郎的枪及帽子的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.85,1:01:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那老婆婆的儿子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:49.06,1:01:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亚迈拉尔达丝心里最爱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:00.73,1:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车长先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:02.07,1:02:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得车子不要停在托列达
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:06.71,1:02:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉亚\n你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:08.98,1:02:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果不照着时间去行驶的话\n我会被革职的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:12.88,1:02:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.21,1:02:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了托列达铁郎就会被\n机械伯爵杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:18.25,1:02:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得车子\n经过托列达就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:24.22,1:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:25.29,1:02:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…该不会喜欢铁郎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:29.16,1:02:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:41.27,1:02:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托列达的分岐点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.91,1:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是每个空间集结之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:47.61,1:02:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙的大分岐点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:50.78,1:02:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅客们一定会经过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:55.39,1:02:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个自由的城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:00.79,1:03:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多男人抱着梦想来到此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:04.56,1:03:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的人变成这片土地的尘土
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.40,1:03:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的人则抱着梦想\n踏上茫茫的宇宙之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:15.04,1:03:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是行星重美尔达
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:25.95,1:03:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎\n没事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:01.55,1:04:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔\n我在附近晃晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:07.99,1:04:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好有人知道时间城
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:11.60,1:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.17,1:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:06.92,1:05:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么星球\n我还是这么爱它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:18.83,1:05:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展翅的鸟儿很像想拥有我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:30.84,1:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如坏掉的玩具箱般的\n像孩子般地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:42.09,1:05:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱着流下泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:48.83,1:05:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那又怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:58.27,1:06:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么星球\n我还是这么爱它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:09.98,1:06:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已极尽疲累的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:15.99,1:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要对它温柔及关心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:22.13,1:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任谁谈到过往种种
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:33.51,1:06:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会很珍惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:40.35,1:06:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那又怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:04.50,1:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太精彩了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:10.54,1:07:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:13.65,1:07:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次来吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:15.85,1:07:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都哭了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:18.08,1:07:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是歌曲的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:20.72,1:07:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家想到无法再次回到的\n年轻过往
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:26.29,1:07:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅途中想喘口气的\n郁郁不乐旅人们会来听
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:35.60,1:07:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要点什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:37.30,1:07:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:40.61,1:07:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他点牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:42.84,1:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小子还没长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:44.74,1:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳臭还未干
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.05,1:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以请我喝一杯牛奶吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:58.59,1:08:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷\n你对这个星球很熟吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:02.66,1:08:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是这个星球的活字典
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:05.06,1:08:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你知道机械伯爵\n什么时候会来这个星球？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:29.79,1:08:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找机械伯爵做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:32.76,1:08:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:33.69,1:08:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\n你不是他的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:38.43,1:08:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打看看怎么会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:40.93,1:08:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械伯爵杀了我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:44.24,1:08:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不只是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:46.21,1:08:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把人类当猎物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:47.57,1:08:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以有很多小孩的父母都被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:50.74,1:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了那些小孩\n我一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:54.75,1:08:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了\n那你去浪夫罗地亚看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:58.28,1:08:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浪夫罗地亚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:59.92,1:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从这里往南走10公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:02.36,1:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里有一位奇怪的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:05.49,1:09:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对机械伯爵的动态很了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.37,1:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:20.74,1:09:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼跑哪去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.71,1:09:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他什么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:24.28,1:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:15.56,1:10:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真烂的破车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:58.30,1:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是…\n他也戴着我做的帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:03.28,1:11:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:05.08,1:11:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么有那顶帽子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:07.15,1:11:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你妈妈给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.48,1:11:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:11.75,1:11:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她把我从危险的地方救出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:15.89,1:11:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:18.82,1:11:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好吗？\n我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:20.66,1:11:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:23.83,1:11:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙飘泊时她常这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:26.23,1:11:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先进来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:28.57,1:11:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:42.21,1:11:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\n你为了此事来找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:48.09,1:11:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我\n机械伯爵什么时候会来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.03,1:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想的跟我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.86,1:11:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:59.30,1:12:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:01.07,1:12:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾是满心热血沸胜的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:06.51,1:12:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是变成机械身躯后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:09.21,1:12:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便开始伤害人类了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:12.85,1:12:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法原谅他们的残酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:19.32,1:12:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.85,1:12:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:23.29,1:12:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\n为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:24.99,1:12:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不行了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:27.63,1:12:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长年在宇宙的飘泊生活\n让我患了宇宙病
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:33.33,1:12:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心\n我不会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:37.40,1:12:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不能死…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:39.37,1:12:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊\n亚迈拉尔达丝也在找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:44.71,1:12:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也遇到亚迈拉尔达丝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:46.81,1:12:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她告诉我时间城的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:52.32,1:12:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在今晚午夜从\n浪夫罗地亚山峰的另一端进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:01.63,1:13:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从浪夫罗地亚的山峰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:04.40,1:13:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在累垮之前\n我想用我的手打倒机械伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:11.10,1:13:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎\n有件事拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:13.34,1:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:14.91,1:13:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住\n等我躺下之后就按下那边操纵杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:19.95,1:13:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按操纵杆做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.72,1:13:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要到某个地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:29.46,1:13:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住铁郎\n要粉碎机械伯爵的头…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:33.69,1:13:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏机械人的头\n他就无法再次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:41.00,1:13:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:42.00,1:13:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:44.57,1:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要变成一种机械
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:48.51,1:13:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘上我亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:51.71,1:13:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成阿尔卡地亚的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:54.75,1:13:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到另一个宇宙星海
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:57.15,1:13:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎\n快按操纵杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:00.25,1:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:04.62,1:14:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还要我下床去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:07.43,1:14:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.49,1:14:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一点\n铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:12.80,1:14:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有很多想做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:12.36,1:15:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类时候到了就会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:16.26,1:15:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你在梦想未完成途中就死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:30.88,1:15:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是机械伯爵的同夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:49.46,1:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回家喝你妈的奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:57.77,1:15:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:38.24,1:16:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪还我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:40.58,1:16:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:51.59,1:16:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还我\n我的枪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:08.81,1:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:12.75,1:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:15.65,1:17:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…虎克船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:23.22,1:17:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爹\n给我牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:35.97,1:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝一杯吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:36.90,1:17:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道错了\n饶了我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:54.05,1:17:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要去吗？\n无论如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:55.99,1:17:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:58.29,1:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要救我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:01.83,1:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我的好朋友盖坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:05.73,1:18:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的好朋友就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:21.31,1:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见\n虎克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:26.22,1:18:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚迈拉尔达丝\n你找的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:30.42,1:18:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,土次郎怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:33.43,1:18:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在这个星球吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:35.59,1:18:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里？虎克
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:41.50,1:18:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:34.29,1:19:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是时间城？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:19.18,1:22:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈…妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:51.08,1:22:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟机械伯爵是同一夥的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:53.22,1:22:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:56.42,1:22:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:57.92,1:22:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫星野铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:59.19,1:23:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要为我妈妈报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:01.89,1:23:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报仇\n凭你要把我打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:06.30,1:23:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:26.99,1:23:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经告诉过你了\n一定要先发致胜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:31.06,1:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安达列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:32.42,1:23:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我乘风而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:44.14,1:23:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\n安达列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:45.17,1:23:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:49.37,1:23:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也为把大家的怨恨出气
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:02.15,1:24:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:03.46,1:24:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.13,1:24:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切交给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:26.41,1:24:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:39.46,1:24:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:41.33,1:24:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体已经变成这样\n我已没有气力决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:45.26,1:24:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再让悲惨的我痛苦下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:53.34,1:24:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安达列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:00.98,1:25:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:05.12,1:25:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切交给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:10.79,1:25:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安达列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:11.72,1:25:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离我远一点\n我身体的未爆弹将会引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:16.16,1:25:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柳织\n快操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:22.23,1:25:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柳织\n你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:23.50,1:25:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点操作时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:36.08,1:25:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柳织！怎么了！柳织
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:41.78,1:25:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最后你的夥伴还是背叛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:44.09,1:25:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:45.42,1:25:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也会被你的同类杀了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:52.43,1:25:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:53.53,1:25:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔…梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:24.33,1:26:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎\n快一点逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:27.60,1:26:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间城快毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:30.17,1:26:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你想救我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:33.84,1:26:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到你\n我想到以前无法挽回的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:39.17,1:26:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唤回以前的意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:41.61,1:26:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的我跟你一样是血肉之躯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:47.35,1:26:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是按照机械伯爵的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:50.75,1:26:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成机械人后\n不断的改造
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:55.19,1:26:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已不是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:59.76,1:27:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是控制时间的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:02.60,1:27:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有一件我能操控的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:06.50,1:27:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是如人类般流着\n温暖血液之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:14.81,1:27:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:18.31,1:27:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体\n你的身体在毁坏中
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:26.56,1:27:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\n柳织
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:55.48,1:28:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要杀伯爵\n我用心对你如此呐喊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:04.53,1:28:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\n这样也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:17.43,1:29:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:23.00,1:30:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你已经报仇了\n铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:32.01,1:30:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎克船长\n你错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:36.11,1:30:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了机械伯爵的机械体\n让我了解长生不老并不算幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:42.22,1:30:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅有的珍贵生命中\n为人努力奋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:45.75,1:30:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才会衍生关怀及温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:48.16,1:30:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于顿悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:49.92,1:30:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械体由整个宇宙中消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:54.33,1:30:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我这种肉体\n永远活在这个世上才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:57.90,1:31:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能拥有机械体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.47,1:31:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:04.37,1:31:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要到安卓美达\n免费供应机械身体的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:09.41,1:31:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想毁掉那个星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:27.83,1:31:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始我还不这么想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:31.03,1:31:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:32.37,1:31:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我坐上银河铁道999列车\n很谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:36.97,1:31:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:55.89,1:31:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:57.79,1:31:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:23.75,1:33:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔\n有什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:25.51,1:33:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:38.03,1:33:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你\n铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:39.76,1:33:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为你妈妈打了漂亮的一仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:47.14,1:33:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:56.68,1:33:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:59.15,1:34:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快到终点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.18,1:34:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一点我蛮在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:02.25,1:34:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像视线渐渐看得见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:05.12,1:34:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:12.66,1:34:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔，梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:14.86,1:34:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是超…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:19.97,1:34:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得旅行这么平静
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:22.37,1:34:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就别管他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:26.44,1:34:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:27.98,1:34:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个旅行结束后回到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:31.48,1:34:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:33.55,1:34:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:35.95,1:34:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:43.16,1:34:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:45.33,1:34:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:11.59,1:35:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎有一天一定会发觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:15.06,1:35:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他所爱的我是藉由\n时空转换来到这里的过去的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:24.33,1:35:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:25.47,1:35:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好珍惜你对铁郎的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:29.27,1:35:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最后为止都不能抱有任何希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:37.65,1:35:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:44.32,1:35:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像着像这样一个人\n乘车旅行的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:49.76,1:35:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！气氛真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:02.47,1:36:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您长久以来的乘车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:05.97,1:36:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:10.71,1:36:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到达的车站是梅德尔行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:13.01,1:36:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:14.92,1:36:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械外表的星球，梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:28.20,1:36:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械化星球的梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:58.15,1:37:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:00.52,1:38:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到达车站是梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:05.26,1:38:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:09.73,1:38:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械外表的梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:18.51,1:38:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:21.01,1:38:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和你的名字相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:24.38,1:38:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:45.00,1:38:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎您回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:46.07,1:38:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:48.24,1:38:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且您平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:50.67,1:38:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您带着的这个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:53.98,1:38:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与您担任负责人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:55.94,1:39:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都可以在\n控制中心的电脑里看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:01.52,1:39:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下由衷地感到非常高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:05.69,1:39:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:06.79,1:39:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:09.52,1:39:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球全是用\n被人类毁坏的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:13.03,1:39:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建造而成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:16.06,1:39:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且我们已经将你从机器上删除
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:21.87,1:39:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经通过测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:23.40,1:39:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们不能认可的重罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:26.77,1:39:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了赎罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:28.58,1:39:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须成为梅德尔星球上的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:32.81,1:39:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续为梅德尔星球效命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:37.72,1:39:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:39.02,1:39:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:49.43,1:39:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真卑鄙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:05.88,1:40:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要往入口那边去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:08.58,1:40:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:36.81,1:40:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:34.27,1:41:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王布罗美修大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:36.14,1:41:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为您带来零件号码第8998982人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:41.21,1:41:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星野铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:43.28,1:41:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:45.41,1:41:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不要成为机械的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:53.12,1:41:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个少年的适性是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:55.19,1:41:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中央机械附近的螺丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:58.23,1:41:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理由是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:00.13,1:42:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个意识强烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:01.40,1:42:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到强烈的惊吓\n也能承受得了的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:06.63,1:42:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要让我…做螺丝吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:08.77,1:42:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，具有心灵的螺丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:11.51,1:42:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支持星球的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:16.24,1:42:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我，放开我，放开我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:20.25,1:42:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:21.48,1:42:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要成为螺丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:23.85,1:42:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:25.39,1:42:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛，放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:28.96,1:42:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙，放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:33.39,1:42:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！不要！不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:35.56,1:42:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽们！\n我不会听从你的命令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:39.30,1:42:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:51.68,1:42:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:52.91,1:42:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来嘲笑我的蠢样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:55.18,1:42:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我女儿说无礼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:57.62,1:42:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是连零件都当不成\n而要被杀死喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:00.05,1:43:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女儿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:00.92,1:43:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造这个机械帝国的女王\n布罗美修唯一的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:06.96,1:43:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:08.76,1:43:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:10.16,1:43:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和机器怪物一起旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:12.83,1:43:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还喜欢上这怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:15.07,1:43:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人不敢置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:16.87,1:43:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，梅德尔也爱着你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:22.21,1:43:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是那时候的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:24.38,1:43:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:25.91,1:43:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，母亲大人，是父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:31.49,1:43:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半机械世界的背叛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:34.79,1:43:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，布罗美修
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:36.69,1:43:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的机器女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:38.99,1:43:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的灵魂以这样的状态回复
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:42.63,1:43:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个能源具有\n足以破坏这个中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:46.17,1:43:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使其残破不堪的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:49.27,1:43:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少说蠢话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:50.94,1:43:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是活着的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:52.71,1:43:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能破坏得了梅德尔行星吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:55.88,1:43:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔也存着疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:57.78,1:44:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为零件究竟是为了什么\n还有要做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:02.35,1:44:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为零件要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:04.45,1:44:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是成为重要的部分\n究竟是为了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:11.19,1:44:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:12.59,1:44:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人跟随着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:14.60,1:44:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理解众人有同样心情的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:17.50,1:44:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了破坏这个机械帝国
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:19.90,1:44:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇见将会牺牲许多的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:22.97,1:44:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我即使想哭也只能忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:24.94,1:44:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望带给那些人很多好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:29.21,1:44:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:30.41,1:44:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想背叛母亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:33.55,1:44:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想对这个给你\n全宇宙最美丽身体的母亲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:42.02,1:44:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能给予永远生命的我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:48.46,1:44:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:49.46,1:44:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便有永不结束的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:52.80,1:44:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得无所谓吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:54.50,1:44:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将这个具有历史的星球加以破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:57.64,1:45:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也活不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:01.38,1:45:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:09.12,1:45:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果机械帝国能灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:11.25,1:45:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:30.50,1:45:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:31.71,1:45:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了面对危险的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:33.24,1:45:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跨越死亡的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:38.65,1:45:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会不会输的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:40.98,1:45:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不战斗的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:44.42,1:45:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎全都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:51.39,1:45:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:52.09,1:45:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:53.93,1:45:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把他平安救出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:55.43,1:45:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:08.88,1:46:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:11.91,1:46:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚迈拉尔达丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:13.51,1:46:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我的身体是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:15.52,1:46:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的灵魂永不会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:18.29,1:46:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样在这里和好朋友一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:20.55,1:46:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在安卡利亚的的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:21.62,1:46:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙的海洋里倘佯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:25.59,1:46:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是多亏了铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:29.23,1:46:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，多次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:31.00,1:46:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会遵从你的愿望\n紧跟着铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:34.64,1:46:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到死都不变
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:56.06,1:46:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止，梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:57.76,1:46:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:59.43,1:47:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点破坏中心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:02.56,1:47:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:03.56,1:47:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到我这边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:05.03,1:47:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想破坏母亲的梦想吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:09.57,1:47:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:11.34,1:47:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:12.91,1:47:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:14.31,1:47:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我另一颗心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:16.48,1:47:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从年轻一直到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:18.51,1:47:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪一个地方…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:21.28,1:47:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它也算是另一个我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:02.02,1:48:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机械人的悲剧继续下去行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:05.66,1:48:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:07.59,1:48:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人努力\n已经成为我心中了不起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:12.20,1:48:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！快点行动啊\n梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:15.20,1:48:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来！来我这儿吧\n梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:24.14,1:48:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:26.41,1:48:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它交给我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:25.01,1:49:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎，你也能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:27.61,1:49:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是抱着那样的目的\n来这里的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:30.78,1:49:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:32.21,1:49:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护众多的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:34.92,1:49:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:37.12,1:49:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:04.61,1:50:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔，快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:15.82,1:50:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么！快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:33.47,1:50:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分离了，分离了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:37.81,1:50:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:39.71,1:50:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:41.92,1:50:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要离开我！\n分离了，分离了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:47.44,1:52:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:49.11,1:52:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔是机器吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:51.85,1:52:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身体是铁郎的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:56.42,1:52:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是以他年轻的姿态出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:00.02,1:53:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不只有一个姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:02.32,1:53:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样得到另一个身体之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:04.62,1:53:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有另一种姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:07.23,1:53:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在时空交错中旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:09.46,1:53:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很像我母亲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:03.58,1:54:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:42.39,1:54:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:55.36,1:55:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:57.00,1:55:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难受，放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:58.87,1:56:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干脆一同共渡黄泉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:00.17,1:56:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:00.93,1:56:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:02.44,1:56:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:04.60,1:56:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你背叛身为你母亲的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:07.41,1:56:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我所有都夺走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:10.51,1:56:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要夺走你的铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:15.25,1:56:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:16.48,1:56:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:18.65,1:56:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:19.99,1:56:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你将来痛苦一辈子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:26.39,1:56:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:30.36,1:56:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:34.03,1:56:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么，放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:38.81,1:56:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎先生，再见！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:43.98,1:56:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:53.42,1:56:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:15.44,1:58:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护你的克莉儿的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:36.39,1:58:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没看过这么悲伤的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:39.39,1:58:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那说不定是克莉儿的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:51.27,1:58:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莉儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:10.59,1:59:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:14.76,1:59:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一天我们还会在某处相遇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:13.15,2:00:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，哈洛克船长
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:15.92,2:00:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，亚迈拉尔达丝女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:50.36,2:00:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么都要走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:51.96,2:00:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是长久以来一直旅行的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:56.86,2:01:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了拿回以前的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:00.30,2:01:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:01.30,2:01:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是冥王星…
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:05.21,2:01:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:12.55,2:01:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还见得到面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:16.65,2:01:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我一定会回到你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:20.19,2:01:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能认不得我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:47.45,2:01:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:48.51,2:01:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是存在你回忆中的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:53.19,2:01:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你少年时期出现的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:57.39,2:01:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青春时代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:59.39,2:03:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:19.54,2:03:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:26.45,2:03:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铁郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:29.25,2:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:33.45,2:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:39.93,2:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:45.93,2:03:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:50.07,2:03:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:03.55,2:04:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:14.13,2:04:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:15.40,2:04:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随同车笛声响起\n留下的美丽回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:19.97,2:04:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:20.93,2:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随同车笛声响起\n回忆随着列车走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:26.11,2:04:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的旅行结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:28.41,2:04:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会再有另一段旅行开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:32.68,2:04:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再会，梅德尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:35.55,2:04:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再会，银河铁道999
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:48.49,2:04:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再会，少年时代
